# ASL Learning Application - Technical Overview
## Real-Time American Sign Language Recognition System

---

## 🎯 **Project Overview**

**ASL Learning Application** is a computer vision-based educational system that enables real-time recognition and learning of American Sign Language (ASL) signs using machine learning and hand tracking technologies.

### **Key Capabilities**
- Real-time hand gesture recognition
- Interactive ASL learning lessons
- Personalized model training
- Multi-modal detection (fingerspelling + custom ASL signs)
- Persistent learning progress tracking

